                the terms of the MIT X11 license and is free for all uses. You may
                see the terms of the license here:
            </TextBlock>
            <TextBlock Margin="0,6,0,0">
                <Hyperlink FontSize="14"
                           Foreground="#FFFDFDFD"
                           ToolTip="http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.html" Click="Hyperlink_Click_1"><Run FontSize="14" Text="http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.html" />
                </Hyperlink>
            </TextBlock>
            <TextBlock Margin="0,12,5,0"
                       FontSize="18"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap">
                Copyright © Gil Yoder 2013
            </TextBlock>

        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</Window>
